SCOPE OF THIS LICENSE

The MIT license above covers the SeatView SITE CODE ONLY: everything in this
repository under src/, scripts/, migrations/, seeds/, the build configuration,
the static venue metadata in data/venues/, and the placeholder seating-chart
SVGs in public/seatmaps/.

It does NOT cover user-uploaded content. Seat-view photos and their metadata
(seat label / performance date / event name / description) that users submit
through the site are shared under the Creative Commons Attribution-NonCommercial
4.0 International license (CC BY-NC 4.0):

    https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc/4.0/

Uploaders confirm they hold the copyright to their photo and agree to the
CC BY-NC 4.0 terms via a mandatory checkbox before submitting (see README
"Upload content license" and prd.md R11 / ADR-5). User-uploaded content is
stored in Cloudflare D1 + R2 at runtime and is never committed to this
repository.

Real venue seating charts may carry their own copyright. The charts shipped in
public/seatmaps/ are LOCALLY-AUTHORED PLACEHOLDERS only; do not commit real
copyrighted seating charts (see CONTRIBUTING.md).
